  "label": "Severan Dusk",
  "description": "This individual is a lean, long-limbed human of middle years, shaped by constant bracing and balance-work and marked by pronounced forearm tendons and callused palms. Brown eyes sit deep beneath heavy brows, set in a narrow face with a straight nose and a weathered jawline. Black hair is kept in a plain, close-cropped style that exposes a high forehead and a slightly uneven hairline. Amber skin bears permanent wind-chap texture across the cheeks and a thin, pale seam at the chin consistent with an old split wound.",
